rComments: Very intense discussions, challenging, a more interesting class than I thought it would be. This kind of class is really what university education should be about.

If you actually visit this prof in her office and talk to her, you'll be surprised by how friendly and helpful she actually is. She'll read the draft of your essay and make extremely helpful comments. She's willing to clarify course concepts in class and out.
